For the June 1991 network, use the iterative correlation clustering method, which takes the correlation of the original adjacency matrix and keeps taking the correlation of this result until it converges to a matrix of 1s and 1s. Use this method to split the network into clusters of cliques, and plot the result. Perform this calculation directly on the matrix.

concor = list()
month61991 = (1991- 1981)*12 + 6
